1) admin-api
  
/users
  POST / - create user
  
/products
  POST / - create project
  
2) customer-api

/products
  GET / - search products
  GET /:id - get product by id

/cart
  GET / - get cart items
  POST / - add product to cart
  DELETE / - remove all cart items

/orders
  POST / - place order
  
/payments
  POST /:id - process payment
  
2) inventory-service

>>>> Functions

GetProduct (productId) 
returns: product information
emits: 
  ProductViewed

GetProducts (searchTerm, limit, offset) 
returns: a list of products matching the filters

IsProductInStock(productId) 
returns: the availability of a product in boolean (true if available and false otherwise)

AddToCart(productId)
returns: nothing if successfully added to card otherwise an error
emits:
  ProductAddedInCart

3) order-service

>>>> Functions

PlaceOrder (CartId) 
returns: placed order details if placed correctly otherwise an error
emits:
  ProductOrdered

4) payment-service

>>>> Functions
